citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 5:30-6:30PM on July
10, 2024. The inspector waited at the facility for the licensee; an adult at the address said the licensee might have had to
stay later at work. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection can be a serious violation of
the AWA and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section
